# Connectors & Data Integration

- Connectors are added via `pac code add-data-source`
- Never edit `src/generated/**` — wrap in provider adapters under `src/services/`
- Complete the planning flow before adding connectors
- Provider pattern: domain contract → mock provider → real provider (adapter over generated service)
- Connection IDs are environment-specific — use deployment settings files
- For local dev, use mock providers or `VITE_USE_MOCK=true`

Full details: `.github/instructions/02-connectors.instructions.md`
